ver Structure\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 18, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 19, \"content\": \"1. Use `get_file_tree` to get an overview of the directory.\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 20, \"content\": \"2. Identify the main entry points (e.g., `main.py`, `index.js`, `app.py`).\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 21, \"content\": \"3. Note the directory structure and any configuration files.\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 22, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 23, \"content\": \"## Phase 2: Analyze Key Files\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 24, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 25, \"content\": \"1. Use `read_file` to read the main entry points identified above.\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 26, \"content\": \"2. Look for import statements to understand dependencies.\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 27, \"content\": \"3. Identify the core abstractions (classes, functions, modules).\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 28, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 29, \"content\": \"## Phase 3: Produce Summary\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 30, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 31, \"content\": \"Combine your findings into a structured summary:\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 32, \"content\": \"\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\", \"line\": 33, \"content\": \"- **Purpose:** What does this project/directory do?\"}, {\"file\": \"agentic/skills/example-ski