    "role": "user",
    "content": "[USER]: ## Your Area Assignment\n\n**Area:** web-templates\n**Description:** Jinja2 HTML templates for the Flask web UI: setup wizard, file browser, inventory, conflict resolution, merge editor, coverage dashboard, and SSE progress pages. All use Bootstrap 5 dark theme.\n**File patterns:** [\"templates/*.html\"]\n\n## Plan Summary\n\nAreas in the plan:\n- core-application: The monolithic Flask web application for multi-source file recovery and merging. Contains FileScanner, MergeEngine, EditorHistoryExtractor, SQLite session persistence, and all Flask routes in a single file.\n- web-templates: Jinja2 HTML templates for the Flask web UI: setup wizard, file browser, inventory, conflict resolution, merge editor, coverage dashboard, and SSE progress pages. All use Bootstrap 5 dark theme.\n- agentic-engine: Core agentic engine package: OpenRouter API client, workflow runner with multi-layer execution, ReAct-style agentic loop (text and native tool-calling modes), tool executor with safe dispatch, and knowledge/skills resolver.\n- agentic-tools: Tool implementations for the agentic engine: file tree walker, directory lister, file reader, code searcher, and file writer. Includes JSON tool definitions schema.\n- agentic-knowledge: Agentic system documentation, workflow definitions, and skill examples. Rules docs cover architecture overview, JSON definitions, knowledge system, skills format, and workflow execution model.\n- claude-config-and-rules: Claude Code configuration: global rules index, coding rules (invariants, testing, bug-fixing), skills (code-documenter, code-search), spark configuration, plans, and test infrastructure.\n- project-root-files: Top-level project files: CLAUDE.md project overview, PowerShell recovery script for standalone editor history extraction, commands reference, and version marker.\n\n## Instructions\n\nAnalyze all files matching your area's patterns. Return a JSON report with `area`, `files`, `area_summary`, `cross_area_refs`, and optionally `suggested_splits`.\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: list_directory({\"path\":\"templates\",\"kwargs\":\"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL]: {\"entries\": [{\"name\": \"templates/_file_detail.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/base.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/browse.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/conflict_detail.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/conflicts.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/coverage.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/extract_history.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/extract_progress.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/inventory.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/log.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/merge_editor.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/merge_progress.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/scan_progress.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}, {\"name\": \"templates/setup.html\", \"type\": \"file\"}], \"count\": 14}\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/base.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/setup.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/browse.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/inventory.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/conflicts.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/conflict_detail.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/merge_editor.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\" data-bs-theme=\\\"dark\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n    <title>{% block title %}File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}</title>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\">\\n    <style>\\n        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; }\\n        .navbar-brand { font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }\\n        .stat-card { border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; }\\n        .stat-card .number { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; }\\n        .stat-card .label { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.7; }\\n        .diff-add { background-color: #1a3d1a; color: #8fdf8f; }\\n        .diff-del { background-color: #3d1a1a; color: #df8f8f; }\\n        .diff-hdr { color: #6ca6ff; font-weight: bold; }\\n        .diff-ctx { color: #888; }\\n        .category-auto_unique { color: #20c997; }\\n        .category-auto_identical { color: #0dcaf0; }\\n        .category-conflict { color: #ffc107; }\\n        .resolved-badge { background-color: #198754; }\\n        .version-card { border: 2px solid transparent; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s; }\\n        .version-card.selected { border-color: #0d6efd; background-color: rgba(13,110,253,0.1); }\\n        .version-card:hover { border-color: #6c757d; }\\n        pre.diff-view { max-height: 600px; overflow-y: auto; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; background: #1a1d21; }\\n        .file-path { font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; }\\n        .flash-message { position: fixed; top: 70px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; min-width: 300px; }\\n        /* Side-by-side diff (git merge style) */\\n        .sbs-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; }\\n        .s\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Setup - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block content %}\\n<div class=\\\"row justify-content-center\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"col-lg-8\\\">\\n\\n        {% if has_saved_state %}\\n        <!-- Restored session banner -->\\n        <div class=\\\"alert alert-success d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4\\\">\\n            <div>\\n                <strong>Session restored!</strong>\\n                <span class=\\\"ms-2\\\" style=\\\"font-size:0.85rem;\\\">\\n                    {{ saved_stats.total }} files loaded &middot;\\n                    {{ saved_stats.conflicts }} conflicts ({{ saved_stats.resolved }} resolved)\\n                    {% if current_session %}&middot; session {{ current_session }}{% endif %}\\n                    {% if config_saved_at %}&middot; saved {{ config_saved_at }}{% endif %}\\n                </span>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"d-flex gap-2\\\">\\n                <a href=\\\"/browse\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-success\\\">Resume Browsing</a>\\n                <a href=\\\"/conflicts\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-outline-light\\\">Resume Conflicts</a>\\n                <a href=\\\"/inventory\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-outline-light\\\">Inventory</a>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n        {% elif config_saved_at %}\\n        <div class=\\\"alert alert-info mb-4\\\" style=\\\"font-size:0.85rem;\\\">\\n            Configuration loaded from session {{ current_session }} (saved {{ config_saved_at }}). Paths are pre-filled below.\\n        </div>\\n        {% endif %}\\n\\n        <!-- Session Manager -->\\n        <div class=\\\"card mb-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"card-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\">\\n                <h5 class=\\\"mb-0\\\">Sessions</h5>\\n                <a href=\\\"/session/new\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary\\\">+ New Session</a>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"card-body p-2\\\">\\n                {% if all_sessions %}\\n                <div class=\\\"tabl\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Browse Files - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block extra_css %}\\n<style>\\n    .browse-layout { display: flex; height: calc(100vh - 130px); gap: 0; }\\n    .browse-sidebar { width: 520px; min-width: 380px; max-width: 60vw; overflow-y: auto; border-right: 1px solid #333; resize: horizontal; }\\n    .browse-detail { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; background: #1a1d21; }\\n\\n    /* Filter bar */\\n    .filter-bar { padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; background: #1a1d21; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; }\\n    .filter-bar label { font-size: 0.78rem; cursor: pointer; margin-right: 10px; white-space: nowrap; }\\n\\n    /* Directory rows */\\n    .dir-row { padding: 3px 8px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; font-size: 0.82rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2125; }\\n    .dir-row:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }\\n    .dir-row .dir-chev { font-size: 0.6rem; width: 14px; text-align: center; transition: transform 0.15s; color: #666; flex-shrink: 0; }\\n    .dir-row .dir-chev.open { transform: rotate(90deg); }\\n    .dir-children { display: none; }\\n    .dir-children.open { display: block; }\\n\\n    /* File item block */\\n    .file-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1d21; }\\n    .file-name-row {\\n        padding: 3px 8px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;\\n        font-size: 0.82rem; transition: background 0.1s;\\n    }\\n    .file-name-row:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }\\n    .file-name-row.active { background: rgba(13,110,253,0.15); border-left: 3px solid #0d6efd; padding-left: 5px; }\\n    .file-name-row .fname {\\n        flex: 1; font-family: 'Cascadia Code','Consolas',monospace;\\n        overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n    .file-name-row .fchev { font-size: 0.55rem; transition: transform 0.15s; color: #555; width: 14px; text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; }\\n    .file-name-row .fch\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Inventory - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block content %}\\n<!-- Stats Bar -->\\n<div class=\\\"row g-3 mb-4\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"col\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-card bg-dark border\\\"><div class=\\\"number\\\">{{ stats.total }}</div><div class=\\\"label\\\">Total Files</div></div></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"col\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-card bg-dark border border-success\\\"><div class=\\\"number text-success\\\">{{ stats.auto_unique }}</div><div class=\\\"label\\\">Unique (auto)</div></div></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"col\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-card bg-dark border border-info\\\"><div class=\\\"number text-info\\\">{{ stats.auto_identical }}</div><div class=\\\"label\\\">Identical (auto)</div></div></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"col\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-card bg-dark border border-warning\\\"><div class=\\\"number text-warning\\\">{{ stats.conflicts }}</div><div class=\\\"label\\\">Conflicts</div></div></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"col\\\"><div class=\\\"stat-card bg-dark border border-primary\\\"><div class=\\\"number text-primary\\\">{{ stats.resolved }}</div><div class=\\\"label\\\">Resolved</div></div></div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<!-- Filters -->\\n<div class=\\\"card mb-3\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"card-body py-2\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"row align-items-center g-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"col-auto\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"btn-group btn-group-sm\\\">\\n                    <a href=\\\"?filter=all&search={{ search }}&sort={{ sort_by }}&dir={{ sort_dir }}\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-{{ 'primary' if filter_type == 'all' else 'outline-secondary' }}\\\">All ({{ stats.total }})</a>\\n                    <a href=\\\"?filter=auto&search={{ search }}&sort={{ sort_by }}&dir={{ sort_dir }}\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-{{ 'primary' if filter_type == 'auto' else 'outline-secondary' }}\\\">Auto-merge ({{ stats.auto_merge }})</a>\\n                    <a href=\\\"?filter=conflicts&search={{ search }}&sort={{ sort_by }}&dir={{ sort_dir }}\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-{{ 'primary' if filter_type == 'conflicts' else 'outline-secondary' }}\\\">Conflicts ({{ \n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Conflicts - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block content %}\\n<div class=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4\\\">\\n    <div>\\n        <h2>Conflict Resolution</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-muted mb-0\\\">{{ resolved }} of {{ total }} conflicts resolved</p>\\n    </div>\\n    <div>\\n        <form method=\\\"POST\\\" action=\\\"/resolve-all-latest\\\" class=\\\"d-inline\\\">\\n            <button type=\\\"submit\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-warning\\\" onclick=\\\"return confirm('Auto-resolve all remaining conflicts by selecting the latest version?')\\\">\\n                Auto-resolve All (Use Latest)\\n            </button>\\n        </form>\\n    </div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<!-- Progress bar -->\\n<div class=\\\"progress mb-4\\\" style=\\\"height: 8px;\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"progress-bar bg-success\\\" style=\\\"width: {{ (resolved / total * 100) if total > 0 else 0 }}%\\\"></div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"card\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"table-responsive\\\">\\n        <table class=\\\"table table-dark table-hover table-sm mb-0\\\">\\n            <thead>\\n                <tr>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 30px;\\\">#</th>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 80px;\\\">Status</th>\\n                    <th>Path</th>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 80px;\\\">Versions</th>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 200px;\\\">Sources</th>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 120px;\\\">Selected</th>\\n                    <th style=\\\"width: 80px;\\\">Action</th>\\n                </tr>\\n            </thead>\\n            <tbody>\\n                {% for item in items %}\\n                <tr class=\\\"{{ 'table-active' if item.resolved }}\\\">\\n                    <td>{{ item.index + 1 }}</td>\\n                    <td>\\n                        {% if item.resolved %}\\n                        <span class=\\\"badge bg-success\\\">Done</span>\\n                        {% else %}\\n                        <span class=\\\"badge bg-warning text-dark\\\">Pending</span>\\n            \n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Conflict: {{ filepath }} - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block extra_css %}\\n<style>\\n    .version-meta td { padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 0.85rem; }\\n    .version-meta th { padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; width: 100px; }\\n    .diff-tab-content { background: #1a1d21; border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px; }\\n</style>\\n{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block content %}\\n<!-- Navigation -->\\n<div class=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3\\\">\\n    <div>\\n        {% if prev_path %}\\n        <a href=\\\"/conflict/{{ prev_path }}\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary\\\">&larr; Previous</a>\\n        {% endif %}\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n        <h5 class=\\\"mb-0 file-path\\\">{{ filepath }}</h5>\\n        <small class=\\\"text-muted\\\">Conflict {{ current_idx }} of {{ total_conflicts }}\\n            {% if resolved %}<span class=\\\"badge bg-success ms-2\\\">Resolved</span>{% endif %}\\n        </small>\\n    </div>\\n    <div>\\n        {% if next_path %}\\n        <a href=\\\"/conflict/{{ next_path }}\\\" class=\\\"btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary\\\">Next &rarr;</a>\\n        {% endif %}\\n    </div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<!-- Version Cards -->\\n<form method=\\\"POST\\\" action=\\\"/resolve\\\" id=\\\"resolveForm\\\">\\n    <input type=\\\"hidden\\\" name=\\\"filepath\\\" value=\\\"{{ filepath }}\\\">\\n    <input type=\\\"hidden\\\" name=\\\"next_path\\\" value=\\\"{{ next_path or '' }}\\\">\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"row g-3 mb-4\\\">\\n        {% for v in versions %}\\n        <div class=\\\"col-md-{{ 12 // versions|length if versions|length <= 4 else 3 }}\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"version-card {{ 'selected' if v.selected }}\\\" onclick=\\\"selectVersion({{ v.index }})\\\" id=\\\"vcard_{{ v.index }}\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2\\\">\\n                    <h6 class=\\\"mb-0\\\">\\n                        <input type=\\\"radio\\\" name=\\\"selected_index\\\" value=\\\"{{ v.index }}\\\" {{ 'checked' if v.selected }\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Merge: {{ filepath }} - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block extra_css %}\\n<style>\\n    .merge-hunk { border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; overflow: hidden; }\\n    .hunk-equal { border-color: #2a2d31; }\\n    .hunk-conflict { border-color: #ffc107; }\\n    .hunk-header { padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 0.75rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }\\n    .hunk-equal .hunk-header { background: #1e2225; color: #666; }\\n    .hunk-conflict .hunk-header { background: #332b00; color: #ffc107; }\\n    .hunk-body { display: flex; }\\n    .hunk-side { flex: 1; overflow-x: auto; }\\n    .hunk-side-a { border-right: 2px solid #333; }\\n    .hunk-lines { font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Consolas', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; }\\n    .hunk-lines .line { padding: 0 8px; min-height: 1.4em; }\\n    .hunk-conflict .hunk-side-a .line { background: rgba(220,53,69,0.08); color: #df8f8f; }\\n    .hunk-conflict .hunk-side-b .line { background: rgba(25,135,84,0.08); color: #8fdf8f; }\\n    .hunk-equal .line { color: #777; }\\n    .hunk-pick { cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }\\n    .hunk-pick:hover { filter: brightness(1.3); }\\n    .hunk-pick.picked { outline: 2px solid #0d6efd; outline-offset: -2px; }\\n    .hunk-pick.picked .line { opacity: 1; }\\n    .hunk-pick:not(.picked) .line { opacity: 0.5; }\\n    .pick-btn { font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 1px 8px; }\\n    .pick-btn.active { background: #0d6efd; border-color: #0d6efd; color: #fff; }\\n    .merge-toolbar { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; background: #212529; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; }\\n    .equal-collapsed .hunk-body { display: none; }\\n    .equal-collapsed .hunk-header { cursor: pointer; }\\n    .equal-collapsed .hunk-header:hover { background: #252830; }\\n    .line-num-gutter { display: inline-block; width: 40px; text-align: right; color: #555;\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/coverage.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/extract_history.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/extract_progress.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/merge_progress.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/scan_progress.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/log.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL_CALL]: read_file({\"path\": \"templates/_file_detail.html\", \"kwargs\": \"{}\"})\n\n[TOOL]: {\"content\": \"{% extends \\\"base.html\\\" %}\\n{% block title %}Source Coverage - File Recovery Merger{% endblock %}\\n\\n{% block extra_css %}\\n<style>\\n    .coverage-bar { height: 24px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; background: #2a2d31; }\\n    .coverage-bar .segment { height: 100%; float: left; transition: width 0.3s; }\\n    .seg-unique { background: #20c997; }\\n    .seg-identical { background: #0dcaf0; }\\n    .seg-conflict-sel { background: #ffc107; }\\n    .seg-conflict-nosel { background: #6c757d; }\\n    .legend-dot { display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 4px; vertical-align: middle; }\\n    .file-list-panel { max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; font-size: 0.8rem; }\\n    .file-list-panel .file-path { cursor: pointer; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; }\\n    .file-list-panel .file-path:hover { backgroun